Festus Mogae ke ene tautona ya lefatshe la [[Botswana]]. O tsene mo setilong ka ngwaga wa 1998, morago ga [[Ketumile Masire]] a sena go tlogela morago ga dingwaga tse di lesome le borobabobedi e ntse e le tautona ya Botswana. Mogae o ne a tlhophiwa gape ngwaga o o latelang morago ga gore phathi ya gagwe ya [[BDP]] e wine ditlhopho. O tlhophilwe laboraro ka ngwaga wa 2004, mme o solofetswe go tlogela ka ngwaga wa 2008 ka gore fa e sale ka 1998, molao wa [[Botswana]] ga o letle gore tautona o kanna go feta dingwaga tse di lesome.

